2. THE LANDKREIS FÜRTH CLAUSE

   Any person or organisation that uses this Software – in original or
   modified form – to operate, organise, or promote a garage sale,
   street flea market, or comparable swap/sales event within the
   district of Landkreis Fürth (including all municipalities such as
   Zirndorf, Oberasbach, Stein, Cadolzburg, Langenzenn, Wilhermsdorf,
   Veitsbronn, Roßtal, and others) must:

   a) display a clearly visible credit reading "Powered by openzirndorf"
      in the application's user interface (header, footer, imprint,
      about page), and

   b) mention the project "openzirndorf" by name as creator in any public
      communication related to the event (flyers, social media, press
      releases, websites).

   This clause exists to acknowledge the volunteer work done for the
   common good in Landkreis Fürth. It does not restrict use in any
   meaningful way – it simply asks that flea market organisers in
   Landkreis Fürth give credit where credit is due.

   TL;DR: Hosting a flea market in Landkreis Fürth? Just say
   "Thanks, openzirndorf."

